<paragraph id="0D382D36FFD1FFCDFF3CFBFD4FFB6373" blockId="35.[151,703,1111,1137]" box="[151,703,1111,1137]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<heading id="56709A5AFFD1FFCDFF3CFBFD4FFB6373" bold="true" box="[151,703,1111,1137]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" reason="1">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFF3CFBFD4FFB6373" bold="true" box="[151,703,1111,1137]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFF3CFBFD4F546373" authority="Parr" authorityName="Parr, 1933 Pseudoscopelus altipinnis Parr" authorityYear="1933" box="[151,528,1111,1137]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="altipinnis">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFF3CFBFD4C8B6373" bold="true" box="[151,463,1111,1137]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Pseudoscopelus altipinnis</emphasis>
Parr
</taxonomicName>
species group
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0D382D36FFD1FFCDFF3CFB084DB263E6" blockId="35.[151,1440,1186,1692]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFF3CFB084C7A63BE" bold="true" box="[151,318,1186,1212]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Composition.</emphasis>
The 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFED6FB094FF463BE" authorityName="Parr, 1933 Pseudoscopelus altipinnis Parr" authorityYear="1933" box="[381,688,1187,1212]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="altipinnis">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFED6FB094FF463BE" box="[381,688,1187,1212]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Pseudoscopelus altipinnis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group is composed of two species: 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFB16FB09480E63BE" authorityName="Parr, 1933 Pseudoscopelus altipinnis Parr" authorityYear="1933" box="[1213,1354,1187,1212]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="altipinnis">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFB16FB09480E63BE" box="[1213,1354,1187,1212]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. altipinnis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFA2DFB094DAB63E6" authorityName="Melo, 2010 Pseudoscopelus paxtoni Melo" authorityYear="2010" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="paxtoni">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFA2DFB094DAB63E6" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. paxtoni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="459D7EBDFFD1FFCDFF6DFB584E2E619E" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="0D382D36FFD1FFCDFF6DFB584E2E619E" blockId="35.[151,1440,1186,1692]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFF6DFB584C02620E" bold="true" box="[198,326,1266,1292]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFE21FB594FFA620E" authorityName="Parr, 1933 Pseudoscopelus altipinnis Parr" authorityYear="1933" box="[394,702,1267,1292]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="altipinnis">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFE21FB594FFA620E" box="[394,702,1267,1292]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Pseudoscopelus altipinnis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group is diagnosed from its congeners by a combination of characteristics: luminescent tissue present as discrete photophores (
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFC11FAB14E9E6236" box="[954,986,1307,1332]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">vs.</emphasis>
completely absent in 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFB49FAB148036236" authorityName="Prokofiev and Kukuev, 2005 Pseudoscopelus aphos Prokofiev and Kukuev" authorityYear="2005" box="[1250,1351,1307,1332]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="aphos">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFB49FAB148036236" box="[1250,1351,1307,1332]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. aphos</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and as vestigial white lines in 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFE0EFAE94F4D625E" authorityName="Prokofiev and Kukuev, 2006 Pseudoscopelus parini Prokofiev and Kukuev" authorityYear="2006" box="[421,521,1347,1372]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="parini">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFE0EFAE94F4D625E" box="[421,521,1347,1372]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. parini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFD8AFAE94F79625E" box="[545,573,1347,1372]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">trf</emphasis>
in a single series of widely spaced photophores, without a medial circular cluster (
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFF5CFAC14C7F6286" box="[247,315,1387,1412]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">vs. trf</emphasis>
on a single row of closely spaced organs, with a medial, circular cluster in the 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFB43FAC148276286" box="[1256,1379,1387,1412]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="scriptus">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFB43FAC148276286" box="[1256,1379,1387,1412]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. scriptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group; absent in the 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFE6EFA394FDF62AE" authorityName="Prokofiev and Kukuev, 2006 Pseudoscopelus astronesthidens Prokofiev and Kukuev" authorityYear="2006" box="[453,667,1427,1452]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="astronesthidens">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFE6EFA394FDF62AE" box="[453,667,1427,1452]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. astronesthidens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFD7CFA394E1262AE" authorityName="Krefft, 1971 Pseudoscopelus scutatus Krefft" authorityYear="1971" box="[727,854,1427,1452]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="scutatus">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFD7CFA394E1262AE" box="[727,854,1427,1452]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. scutatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species groups; in a broad band of three or four photophores in 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFEE5FA114CA362D6" box="[334,487,1467,1492]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lavenbergi">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFEE5FA114CA362D6" box="[334,487,1467,1492]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. lavenbergi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFDAAFA114F6F62D6" box="[513,555,1467,1492]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">mxf</emphasis>
in an irregular elongated single row with widely spaced photophores anteriorly, extending from below mid-eye anteriorly and connected to 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFC0BFA494E8262FE" box="[928,966,1507,1532]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">apf</emphasis>
posteriorly (
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFBF6FA49493962FE" box="[1117,1149,1507,1532]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">vs.</emphasis>
both 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFB6BFA4949AE62FE" box="[1216,1258,1507,1532]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">mxf</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFA8FFA49480E62FE" box="[1316,1354,1507,1532]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">apf</emphasis>
absent in the species of the 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFE2CF9A14F406126" authorityName="Krefft, 1971 Pseudoscopelus scutatus Krefft" authorityYear="1971" box="[391,516,1547,1572]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="scutatus">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFE2CF9A14F406126" box="[391,516,1547,1572]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. scutatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group; 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFD10F9A14FA16126" box="[699,741,1547,1572]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">mxf</emphasis>
absent and 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFCDAF9A14ED26126" box="[881,918,1547,1572]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">apf</emphasis>
present in 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFBBCF9A149F46126" box="[1047,1200,1547,1572]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lavenbergi">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFBBCF9A149F46126" box="[1047,1200,1547,1572]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. lavenbergi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFB6BF9A149AE6126" box="[1216,1258,1547,1572]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">mxf</emphasis>
short, not connected posteriorly with 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFE05F9994C90614E" box="[430,468,1587,1612]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">apf</emphasis>
present in the species of the 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFC87F9994945614E" authorityName="Prokofiev and Kukuev, 2006 Pseudoscopelus astronesthidens Prokofiev and Kukuev" authorityYear="2006" box="[812,1025,1587,1612]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="astronesthidens">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFC87F9994945614E" box="[812,1025,1587,1612]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. astronesthidens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group; 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFB11F99949A0614E" box="[1210,1252,1587,1612]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">mxf</emphasis>
on single elongate continuous row from level of posterior margin of eye anteriorly to angle between preopercle and dentary, and 
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFF63F9294DAA619E" box="[200,238,1667,1692]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">apf</emphasis>
absent in the species of the 
<taxonomicName id="CA8756B5FFD1FFCDFD9CF9294FF5619E" box="[567,689,1667,1692]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="scriptus">
<emphasis id="3FF3F124FFD1FFCDFD9CF9294FF5619E" box="[567,689,1667,1692]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">P. scriptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group).
</paragraph>
